title: Make a bit faster
message:
Make a bit faster

 - Removes toggleButton.isChecked() as the call wasn’t on the main
thread. Instead, the boolean toggleButtonIsChecked now contains the
contents of toggleButton.isChecked(), so we can call it asynchronously.
Also, I updated comments to explain what was happening, and closed the
database after we have written to it.
